This webpage is a simple yet attractive design inspired by Nykaa, a popular beauty and cosmetics brand. The page highlights the brand name in bold, eye-catching pink text at the center, surrounded by various beauty products such as nail polishes, makeup brushes, and sponges. The navigation bar at the top provides easy access to categories, brands, fashion, and beauty advice, along with a search bar and login button for user convenience. The central “Shop Now” button encourages visitors to explore products further, making the design both user-friendly and visually appealing. Overall, this webpage creates a clean and modern shopping experience with a strong focus on beauty and style
